==French==

===Verb===
'''hacher'''
# To [[chop]] (with a knife)
#:''Hacher la viande.''
#::''Chop up the meat.''
# To [[mince]]; to mince up
#:''Boeuf haché''
#::''Minced beef.''
# To [[break up]]; to [[take apart]]
#:''Je doir hacher la phrase pour qu'ils la comprennent.''
#::''I have to break the sentence up so thay can understand it.''

